verbose_text: Trisomy 12, 13q14 deletion, 6q21 deletion, 11q23 deletion, 17p13 deletion, CD38 expression, ZAP70 expression, CLLU1 expression, NOTCH1 mutation, and SF3B1 mutation statuses were determined in a subset of UK-CLL-1 patients who were participants in the LRF CLL4 Trial, as previously described.
